      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne, ¶ 28 July 1887. ¶ The honorable Alfred Deakin, M.L.A., ¶ Chief Secretary. ¶ Sir,...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">87.07.28</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Alfred Deakin<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">J87/6693, unit 272, VPRS 3992/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">28 July 1887.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The honorable Alfred Deakin, M.L.A.,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Chief Secretary.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In reply to a question by Joseph Harris Esq., M.L.A., asked in the Legislative Assembly yesterday,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Argus</seg>, 28 July 1887, p. 5, col. f.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I have the honor to report, that the descriptive portion of the "Key to the system of Victorian plants" (pt. I), will be ready in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">August</hi>
               </seg>; the completion of the work in a conscientious manner according to the difficult dichotomous method required, for this work, involved far more time than anticipated, the Flora of Victoria being doubly as rich as that of Britain, where not even yet a work according to the Lamarckian method exists for the native plants. I avail myself of this opportunity of soliciting, that the Gov. Printing Department be instructed to push the work in Aug. and September throught the press with every possible speed; but no manuscript can be sent, until the whole is written<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and elaborated, on account of the particular connected<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">numbering</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>required throughout.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The published work was not issued until November 1888 (B88.11.02).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your obed. servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
